Ethnic '''[[Georgians]] in the [[Netherlands]]''' number around 2000, according to 2006 official census.<ref>[http://diaspora.gov.ge/index.php?lang_id=GEO&sec_id=64&info_id=142 Georgians in the Netherlands]</ref><ref>[http://netherlands.mfa.gov.ge/ Embassy of Georgia to The Kingdom of the Netherlands]</ref>  However, Georgian citizens numbered 544 in 2016.

This number does not include the number of Georgians from Iran and the larger number of Georgians from Turkey.
